  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Find answers to the most common questions about the services we offer at Global Services and Maintenance."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Why Choose Global Services and Maintenance?',
        description:
          "At Global Services and Maintenance, we are committed to providing high-quality cleaning and maintenance services. Our highly trained and dedicated team strives to exceed our customers' expectations on every job. Additionally, our attention to detail and eco-friendly approach set us apart in the market.",
      },
      {
        title: 'What Services Do You Offer?',
        description:
          'We offer a wide range of cleaning and maintenance services, including general cleaning, window cleaning, carpet washing, and garden maintenance. Whatever your needs, we are here to help you keep your space clean and tidy.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How Can I Schedule an Appointment?',
        description:
          "Scheduling an appointment with Global Services and Maintenance is easy. Simply get in touch with our team, and we will be happy to coordinate an appointment that fits your schedule. Whether it's for a one-off clean or regular maintenance, we are here to assist.",
      },
      {
        title: 'How Soon Can I Schedule a Service?',
        description:
          "We strive to provide quick and efficient service to our customers. Depending on availability, we can schedule an appointment in as little as a few days. Contact us today, and we'll have your space sparkling clean in no time!",
      },
      {
        title: 'Do You Offer Customised Services?',
        description:
          "Yes, at Global Services and Maintenance, we understand that every customer has unique needs. That's why we offer customised services to accommodate your specific requirements. Just let us know what you need, and we'll design a tailored cleaning and maintenance plan for you!",
      },
      {
        title: 'How Can I Get More Information About Your Services?',
        description:
          'For more information about our services and rates, feel free to contact our team. We are here to answer all your questions and provide you with the information you need to make the best decision for your space.',
      },
    ]}
  />
